# BlueSky Scenario A1: Head-On Approach (Cooperative)
# Edmonton Area B (suburban): Ownship at 53.5200, -113.6000 heading East
# Intruder INT-C01 (C-GABC, Cessna 172): starts at 53.5200, -113.5500 heading West
# Initial separation: ~4.2 km horizontal, 22m vertical
# Per ASTM F3442 integration test plan scenario A1

00:00:00.00>POLY EDM_A1_BOX 53.5100,-113.6100 53.5100,-113.5400 53.5300,-113.5400 53.5300,-113.6100
00:00:00.00>COLOR EDM_A1_BOX 0,255,0

00:00:00.00>TRAILS ON
00:00:00.00>RESO OFF
00:00:00.00>RTF 10
00:00:00.00>PAN 53.5200,-113.5750
00:00:00.00>-

# Intruder INT-C01: Cessna 172, ADS-B Out, heading 270 (West) at 400 ft, 87 kts
