# Format: CRE <acid>,<type>,<lat>,<lon>,<hdg>,<alt>,<spd>
00:00:00.00>CRE INTA1,C172,53.5200,-113.5500,270,400,87
00:00:00.00>INTA1 ADDWPT 53.5200,-113.5750
00:00:00.00>INTA1 ADDWPT 53.5200,-113.6000
